From individuals to companies, it's over with just Achakey!

* You can purchase the product first and install it in the vehicle, or you can use the watch and app only in vehicles that have already been shipped with a smart box installed.

* Support for Android, iOS devices
* We will keep you updated for quality.

[Mandatory authority]
■ Approximate location: Use vehicle parking location, driving history, block zone, auto door lock function
■ Accurate location: Use vehicle parking location, driving history, block zone, auto door lock function
■ Location authority: Use vehicle parking position, driving history, block zone, auto door lock function
※ If you don't allow required rights, it's difficult to use the app's major services normally.

[Choose permission]
■ Phone: Required when using the Lock Screen Control (Lock Screen) function.
■ Camera: To use QR code login, you can choose whether to access the camera or not.
■ ActivityRecognition: The Driving History feature displays more accurate information about the start and end of driving.
※ Major services are available, even if you do not agree to allow selective access
